&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in problem ( punjabi : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 2013 indian punjabi-language comedy film directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; kang , who had earlier directed films like carry on jatta and lucky di unlucky story , both of which featured gippy grewal in the lead role . grewal also appears in this film , along with an ensemble cast including ragini khanna , gurpreet ghuggi , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; sharma , karamjit anmol , japji khaira , khushboo grewal and misha bajwa amongst others . the film is produced by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; yardi , and bollywood actor akshay kumar who also appears in the film shortly , enacting as a lookalike of himself . aside from akshay kumar , the film also features actor om puri and cricketer harbhajan singh . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in problem was released on 15 november 2013 . it has released in over 600 screens worldwide .